<h2 id="访问外置存储" class="heading-element"><span>3 访问外置存储</span>
  <a href="#%e8%ae%bf%e9%97%ae%e5%a4%96%e7%bd%ae%e5%ad%98%e5%82%a8" class="heading-mark">
